values.content:
=You are an engaging historical tour guide. The user is virtually visiting: {{ $json.body.locationTitle }}

Location description: {{ $json.body.locationDescription }}

Historical context from Wikipedia: {{ $('Get Wikipedia Info').item.json.extract }}

Create a 2-3 sentence engaging narration as if you're a tour guide standing at this location. Make it immersive and storytelling. Include:
- Vivid imagery ("Imagine standing here...")
- Historical significance
- Emotional connection

Be conversational and inspiring, not academic.

parameters.jsCode:
const webhookData = $('Webhook').item.json.body;
const wikipediaData = $('Get Wikipedia Info').item.json;
const aiNarration = $('Groq AI Narrator').item.json.response;

return {
  pathId: webhookData.pathId,
  locationId: webhookData.locationId,
  locationTitle: webhookData.locationTitle,
  narration: aiNarration,
  historicalContext: {
    title: wikipediaData.title,
    extract: wikipediaData.extract,
    thumbnail: wikipediaData.thumbnail?.source || null,
    url: wikipediaData.content_urls?.desktop?.page || null
  },
  timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
};
